      <h1  class="pt-2">
  Interview Questions ctd.</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr>

  Please add additional questions from your interview that were not included on the previous page. If submitting new questions not listed in the dropdowns, please classify each quesiton as general, behavioral, or case based on the guidelines in the BTG Handbook. 

  Some addtional guidelines:
  <ul>
    <li>
      If adding a new behavioral question, please use the standard format "TMAT...". For example, "TMAT you failed"
    </li>
    <li>
      Avoid using company names for general and behavioral questions. You can add additional details in the comments section on the next page. For example, rather than "Why do you want to work for Adobe?" please enter "Why do you want to work for this company?"
    </li>
  </ul>


<div class="collapse.show" id="collapseExample">
  <div class="card card-body">
  <div>
    <div>

      <form action="/insert_question" method="post">
        <% loop_count=1%>
        <% while loop_count<=@num_of_new%>
          <strong>Question <%=loop_count%>:</strong>

            <div class="mb-1">
            <label for="new_q">Select from commonly asked questions:</label>
            <select class="form-select mb-3 w-50" id="new_q_<%=loop_count%>" name="new_q_<%=loop_count%>">
              <option selected value="0"></option>
              <%@questions_list=Question.all.order({:text=>:asc})%>
              <%@questions_general=@questions_list.where({:question_type=>"General"})%>
              <%@questions_behavioral=@questions_list.where({:question_type=>"Behavioral"})%>
              <%@questions_case=@questions_list.where({:question_type=>"Case"})%>
              <%@questions_general_text=@questions_general.uniq{|question| [question.text]}%>
              <%@questions_behavioral_text=@questions_behavioral.uniq{|question| [question.text]}%>
              <%@questions_case_text=@questions_case.uniq{|question| [question.text]}%>
              <optgroup label="General:">
                <%@questions_general_text.each do |a_question|%>
                <option value="<%=a_question.id%>"><%=a_question.text%></option>
                <%end%>
              </optgroup>
              <optgroup label="Behavioral:">
                <%@questions_behavioral_text.each do |a_question|%>
                <option value="<%=a_question.id%>"><%=a_question.text%></option>
                <%end%>
              </optgroup>
              <optgroup label="Case:">
                <%@questions_case_text.each do |a_question|%>
                <option value="<%=a_question.id%>"><%=a_question.text%></option>
                <%end%>
              </optgroup>
            </select>
            </div>
          Or submit a new question not listed:
          <div class="input-group mb-3">
          <select type="button" class="form-select btn btn-outline-secondary w-25" id="new_q_number" name="new_q_type_<%=loop_count%>">
          <option selected>Question Type</option>
            <option value="General">General</option>
            <option value="Behavioral">Behavioral</option>
            <option value="Case">Case</option>
          <input class="form-control w-75" id="text_box_<%=loop_count%>" name="new_question_<%=loop_count%>" placeholder="Type new question here"></input>
          </div>
          <hr>
          <%loop_count=loop_count+1%>
        <%end%>
        <%final_count=loop_count-1%>
        <input name="loop_count" type="hidden" value=<%=final_count%>>
        <input name="company_id" type="hidden" value=<%=@company_id%>>
        <input name="role_id" type="hidden" value=<%=@role_id%>>
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Next</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  

